quran[52]{c,v,t}:
  68,1,S wamru akked wayen pjerriden
  68,2,"Keçç, s l$it n Mass ik, ur telliv d aôehbani"
  68,3,"Ih, i keçç arraz ur nepnegzay"
  68,4,"Ih, keçç, lxaîeô ik d ûûam"
  68,5,"A pwaliv, ad walin"
  68,6,anwa degwen ippuhewwlen
  68,7,"D Mass ik, ih, i Izôan sennig wiyav, anwa iff$en abrid iS. D Neppa i Izôan, sennig wiyav, anwi ipwanhan"
  68,8,"Ihi, ur ppak awal i inekkaôen"
  68,9,"Ssaramen a ppestaâmlev, akken ad staâmlen"
  68,10,Ur ssemêas i yal afuêan ipgallan
  68,11,aqeôôad ileêêun iplemmim
  68,12,"i igelden lxiô, ippawven, idenben"
  68,13,"amjuô, u irna d akluc"
  68,14,"Xas $uôes ayla, igwerdan"
  68,15,"Ma $ôan as issekniyen nne£, iqqaô: \"d timucuha imezwura"
  68,16,A t Nweccem deg wanzaren
  68,17,"Ih, Njeôôeb iten akken Njeôôeb at leonan, mi gullen, ar di tûebêit, ad $elten"
  68,18,Ggulen ur êniten
  68,19,"Tezzi yas tbucivant s$uô Mass ik, nitni îîsen"
  68,20,Iu$al amzun d lbuô
  68,21,Di tûebêit msawalen
  68,22,"ekkret zik, ar lexla nnwen, ma a p$elltem"
  68,23,"Teddun, sbecbucen garasen"
  68,24,"igellil, assa, ur t ppaooat a p id ikçem\". ö"
  68,25,"Öuêen ppeklen, zemren"
  68,26,"Mi t walan, nnan: \"nekwni d im$eôôqen"
  68,27,"Ih, aql a$ nepwaêeôôem"
  68,28,"Inna uêdiq mavi nnsen: \"day ur awen nni$ ara: a lemmer tesbuccuâem"
  68,29,"Nnan: \"nesbuccaâ Mass nne$. Nella, s tidep, d imednas"
  68,30,"Mqabalen, ppemyuzzamen"
  68,31,"Nnan: \"a ssexv nne$, nella d imjuôen"
  68,32,"Ahat Mass nne$ ad a$ d I$ôem sennig waya; ih, nekwni, ar Mass nne$, d imectaqen"
  68,33,"Am akka, aqeîîi. Aqeîîi n laxeôt, war ccekk, meqqweô kteô, lemmer éôin"
  68,34,"Ih, i wid ipêezziben i Mass nnsen, Loennet n ssuâada"
  68,35,Aâni Nerr imvuâen am ibe$wviyen
  68,36,Acu ikwen iu$en? Amek tepêuddum
  68,37,Ne$ tesâam tazmamt ideg tlemdem
  68,38,"degs, i kunwi, s tidep, ayen tesmenyafem"
  68,39,"Ne$ $uôwen tuqqna s$uône$, ar ass iqeîîiten, ara kwen id ias wayen têuddem"
  68,40,"Steqsi ten ma, $ef waya, $uôsen îîamen"
  68,41,"ne$ $uôsen icriken? Ihi, a d awin icriken nnsen, ma d tidep ay ssawalen"
  68,42,"Ass ideg ara tepwafveê twa$it, ad asen inin ad knun, ur zmiren"
  68,43,"Ad brunt wallen, ddell iwwet iten. Ni$ pwanecden ar lekni, mi llan ûeêêan"
  68,44,"Eoo iyI akked wid iskaddben awal agi. Ad asen Ddu$ cwiî, cwiî, seg wanda ur éôin"
  68,45,Ad asen Fke$ lmudda. Ni$ tiêeôci W teéweô
  68,46,"Ne$ tessutrev taqdiât, fellasen d îîlaba ééayen"
  68,47,"Ne$ $uôsen tabavnit, d$a la pparun"
  68,48,"Eûbeô i ôôay n Mass ik, ur ppili am bu uslem, i d issawlen mi ippuêeyyeô"
  68,49,"Lemmer ur t id issukkes l$it n Mass is, a d iu$al ar lxali, d amaâfun"
  68,50,"Ifren it Mass is, Irra t seg iâaôviyen"
  68,51,"Qôib i k smalen ijehliyen, s wallen nnsen, mi slan i usmekti. La qqaôen: \"ar neppa d aôehbani"
  68,52,"Neppa, d asmekti kan i imavalen"